data.description:
Nice Boise Home in Plantation View Estates
3 Bedrooms
2 Full Baths
1287 square feet
$1695.00 Per Month Rent
$1695.00 Security Deposit
NO Pets
Available august 1, 2021
Lease Term 1 year 
Quiet Cul De Sac
Fully Fenced Back Yard with Storage Shed
Fenced Side Yard Perfect for RV Parking
NO SMOKING
Dogs OK with approval and pet fee 
Washer and Dryer Hook Up available in Home
For more information or to schedule a showing contact Keri at Address is:
5803 W Ohara Ct
Boise 83703
Located off of State Street and Ellens Ferry
One on One Showings scheduled only with pre approved applicants.

Tenant responsible for all utilities and lawn care.
